<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhōng guó rén yào qǐ lái 迦南184</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhōng guó zhōng guó zhōng guó rén yào qǐ lái, chén mò duō shǎo nián, hūn shuì duō shǎo zài,
 jīn rì yào xiàng měng shī sū xǐng. zhōng guó zhōng guó zhōng guó rén yào qǐ lái,
 wǒ men tóng xīn wèi nǐ zhù fú, wǒ men qí shēng xiàng nǐ hē cǎi,
 wàn jūn zhī shén yǒng yuǎn ài nǐ, zhōng guó zhōng guó zhōng guó rén yào qǐ lái.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>184</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>